### Running in node

* Compile your program with: ghcjs Hello.hs
* node Hello.jsexe/all

### Running interactive in the Browser

* Install socket.io

~~~
npm install -g socket.io
~~~

* Start interactive ghcjs session

~~~
ghcjs --interactive
~~~    

* Connect from the browser to ghcjs

~~~
http://localhost:6400
~~~